                                ex unde quo eveniet distinctio qui sunt magnam
                                ad unde voluptate.
                            </p>
                            <div class="card-pictures_container">
                                <div class="adaptive-img--cover card_pictures">
                                    <span>
                                        <img
                                            src="{{
                                                asset(
                                                    'assets/images/trek_snow.jpg'
                                                )
                                            }}"
                                            alt="Trek dans les montagnes enneigées"
                                        />
                                    </span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="adaptive-img--cover card_pictures">
                                    <span>
                                        <img
                                            src="{{
                                                asset(
                                                    'assets/images/trek_bivouac.jpg'
                                                )
                                            }}"
                                            alt="Bivouac dans les montagnes"
                                        />
                                    </span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="yellow-btn_container">
                                <a href="/prices">Voir les tarifs</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </article>

                    <article class="trail">
                        <div class="activity-card" id="trail-card">
                            <h3>Trail</h3>
